    CREATE TABLE level (
        levelID INT AUTO_INCREMENT PRIMARY KEY,
        levelname VARCHAR(255),
        level_categoryID INT,
        FOREIGN KEY (level_categoryID) REFERENCES level_category(level_categoryID)
    )
    """

        levelID INT,
        FOREIGN KEY (levelID) REFERENCES level(levelID)
    )
